            Produced by <a href="http://outerearth.net">Outer Earth Interactive</a>.
        </p>
        <p>
            <a href="/new" class='btn btn-primary btn-large'><i class="icon-file-alt"></i> Create a Document</a> or <a href="/upload" class='btn btn-large'><i class="icon-cloud-upload"></i> Upload a File</a> or <a href="/documentation" class='btn btn-info btn-large'><i class="icon-eye-open"></i> View Javascript Documentation</a>
